    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>The cookbook looks great! I hope you&#8217;ll be having a signing here in town. Maybe even at Secret Garden, or even better, the Ballard Farmer&#8217;s Market! But I really wanted to extend an additional congragulations on Brandon&#8217;s mention by restaurant reviewer Leslie Kelly in the Seattle PI. <a href="http://seattlepi.nwsource.com/food/394942_dining07.html" rel="nofollow ugc">http://seattlepi.nwsource.com/food/394942_dining07.html</a></>I almost posted a response asking &#8220;Hey Leslie, do you KNOW who his wife is?&#8221; but I figured if she doesn&#8217;t, she&#8217;ll know soon enough!</p>
