    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Congratulations Molly on your book. It&#8217;s a lovely image for the cover.  I can&#8217;t wait to order and read it.</></>Your post made me think about going to a local coffee shop every morning to get coffee and a bagel.  My boss always asked for a bagel with cream cheese and celery seasoning.  I thought this an odd request, but the local shop went out and bought it just so my boss could get what he asked for. </></>Other than celery w/ peanut butter I hadn&#8217;t thought of a dish like this. I can&#8217;t wait to try to make it.</p>
    </div>

