    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Molly,</></>I couldn&#8217;t agree more with your description of celeri root remoulade. It is so, so simple and one would think by the looks of it, so, so pedestrian. Au contraire! I remember eating many a small plate during visits to Paris and wishing for seconds, and thirds&#8230;. It is one of the most delicious salads I have ever, ever eaten. Thanks for reminding me!Congratulations on your book deal. I love reading your column in Bon Appetit as well!</p>
